title: Match History Bug?
body:
Not sure if this is the correct place for this type of issue...

So this is actually a bug I'm having on the League of Legends website (NA Server) where when I go to see my match history via browser (Using Chrome) it doesn't load. It gives me a sort of white box that has the outlines of the match history box but nothing loads inside of it (Can add picture if needed). Never had this happen before and re-logging doesn't seem to fix the issue. 

Thanks!

replies.body:
This sometimes happens on the Match History section of the site. I recommend trying incognito mode, a different browser, or [clearing your browser cache](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies).

Let me know if any of those steps worked.
Clearing the cache fixed the issue. Thank you!
